{"tid":715340,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"溫野菜 食評","createTime":"2018-06-24T12:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T19:48:53.000Z","uid":175988,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb68a8ec66eab203645f573547fbf7de5146a9f","tid":715340,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>溫野菜 @ Festival Walk</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lu4IW3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flu4IW3c.jpg&h=33ced274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/balBgD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbalBgD3.jpg&h=3caa3fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>火鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配菜質感唔錯，紅心蘿蔔腍中帶爽脆，南瓜粉糯無渣，略嫌鮮甜味唔夠<br />\n<br />\n豆乳湯底順滑，豆味濃郁又唔會蓋過食材味道<br />\n<br />\n黑松露雞肉夾雜軟骨，鬆軟而有口感，不過松露味薄弱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部肉類 (包括牛同雞) 都肉味不足，雪味過重，且份量偏少<br />\n<br />\n雜菌燴飯欠缺調味，突出唔到菇嘅鮮味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 推介俾鍾意食菜嘅人 or 素食者，肉食真心非常普通且唔抵，與其加百幾蚊轉日本黑毛和牛，我寧願食一般火鍋店嘅手切肥牛好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"318571c24282e66bebdc35fd3e6fc77eb3a84a5b","tid":715340,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39af97b208f4dfb443d8d7a8631467fb9a58fda9","tid":715340,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e91fa9000121ee1ce6020b59aaf88d7f287acd","tid":715340,"uid":71748,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:11:54.000Z","msg":"咪又係牛角"},{"pid":"26157d9f3ca37fad2461850eda21ea1f5854ee12","tid":715340,"uid":62222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"用匯豐卡有折會抵啲既<br />\n但一次就夠<br />\n無咩特別"},{"pid":"f70a9a028517eca759e5ef7f01e1ea27e245e5b6","tid":715340,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:48:53.000Z","msg":"溫野菜係日本先抵食"}]}